Title: mk_oracle: New default hostname in GI/Restart configurations
Level: 1
Component: checks
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
Version: 1.6.0b1
Date: 1559635589
Class: feature

The old design used localhost as default connection host when
DBHOST is empty in mk_oracle.cfg. This has been changed from
localhost to $(hostname) for configurations with Grid-Infrastructure
or Oracle Restart
